title: California Coastal Commission bans SeaWorld orca breeding, tanks can expand
text: Actress Pamela Anderson speaks during a PETA protest of Sea World’s proposed expansion plans for an orca habitat called Blue World. The proposal is up for a vote at the California Coastal Commission meeting. BRITTANY MURRAY — STAFF PHOTOGRAPHER
